NetShield provides real-time network security monitoring, DNS filtering,
device management, traffic inspection, and threat intelligence for OPNsense.

Features:
- Deep packet inspection and application identification
- DNS-based content filtering with category and parental controls
- GeoIP-based traffic blocking
- Device tracking and quarantine enforcement
- Behavioral IDS with threat feed integration
- Multi-VPN profile management (Fusion VPN)
- Mobile JWT API for remote monitoring
- Tor exit node auto-blocking
- Web category filtering
- Real-time bandwidth and session monitoring
- Telegram alert notifications

WWW: https://github.com/netshield-project/os-netshield
